                <h1>Construction update: Southgate, Epworth to close for 2018-19 academic year, Crowell Quad set to re-open</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/9b90d775-acd2-4935-b285-e9db8697f2a3.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Construction&#x20;continues&#x20;on&#x20;the&#x20;Hollows&#x20;quad.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
